  <name>Ferrix</name>
  <summary>Swiss Knife for Linux hardware diagnostics</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Ferrix is a program for obtaining information about computer hardware and software. It is designed to work in modern Linux OS distributions, written in Rust using GTK4 and libadwaita.</p>
  </description>

  <developer id="tld.vendor">
    <name>Michail Krasnov</name>
  </developer>

